{"tid":2201621,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"劉兆佳：12人送中案件符合国安法中 可移交中共審理的「特殊情况」","createTime":"2020-09-14T02:57:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T04:17:46.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f1bba5c17244d58c655d2e4c798b2b8cc62fe460","tid":2201621,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T02:57:46.000Z","msg":"劉兆佳表示，中央非常重視案件，欲調查被捕人背後的勢力和資金，不排除20多日盤問中獲得他們違反國安法的罪行及新證據。劉又稱該12人中有人棄保潛逃，拒絕到港法院應訊，顯示在港處理案件「有一定難度」，符合港區國安法中可交內地審理的「特殊情况」（見另稿）。據了解，該12人由何人組織及牽線上船偷渡，屬內地偵查有否違國安法的範圍之一。<br />\n<br />\n梁美芬表示，《港區國安法》屬全國法律，中港兩地均有管轄權，且兩地沒有移交逃犯協定，形容該12名港人「自投羅網」，認為他們在內地接受審訊的可能較高，港府在此事上沒太多話語權，最終由內地有關部門決定。<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20200914/s00001/1600020792143/</code></pre>"},{"pid":"2dfa754bf169435d96d50957f320fae02394ac7e","tid":2201621,"uid":365024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T02:58:04.000Z","msg":"Hi 張醫生"},{"pid":"5f625c3d868d8c8f12874f713388462269269093","tid":2201621,"uid":93600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T02:58:05.000Z","msg":"送中了"},{"pid":"6351a65173ffa92049078ad0dcd87aa4520ac246","tid":2201621,"uid":41873,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T02:58:38.000Z","msg":"南海係中國領土？"},{"pid":"53e11409ae199877cb4b43cb0a8b3dcf7173eb22","tid":2201621,"uid":290118,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T02:58:57.000Z","msg":"以後乜撚都話特殊情况<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc19ef21572c80d85940387cdf82b1c28340043b","tid":2201621,"uid":47697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T02:58:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"512d562c9edeb2f20d0bcf9f6ed4ca26b6209c82","tid":2201621,"uid":290118,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6351a65173ffa92049078ad0dcd87aa4520ac246","tid":2201621,"uid":41873,"like":2,"disli